{"id":2315,"date":"2021-04-01T10:18:32","date_gmt":"2021-04-01T10:18:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/?p=2315"},"modified":"2021-10-05T03:07:34","modified_gmt":"2021-10-05T03:07:34","slug":"cach-nau-yen-sao-bau-ngu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/cach-nau-yen-sao-bau-ngu\/","title":{"rendered":"3 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o v\u00e0 b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 ngon nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o<\/a> v\u00e0 b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cao. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f3n \u0103n ngon, b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn t\u1eeb 2 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Lifenest s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn <\/span><b>y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, d\u1ec5 l\u00e0m, c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i nh\u00e9.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>3 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a 18 lo\u1ea1i axit amin, nhi\u1ec1u vitamin, protein c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1m, ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o, 19 lo\u1ea1i axit amin \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 threonine, valin, isoleucine, axit glutamic c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vitamin B1, B2, paolin,\u2026\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00f3n \u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn t\u1eeb y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o v\u00e0 b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn ngu\u1ed3n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o, gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y sinh l\u1ef1c. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn m\u00f3n \u0103n t\u1eeb y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>1. Ch\u00e1o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 v\u1edbi y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2317\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2317\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2317 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-1.jpg\" alt=\"Ch\u00e1o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-1.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-1-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-1-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2317\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ch\u00e1o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o<\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">100 gram g\u1ea1o n\u1ebfp v\u00e0 g\u1ea1o t\u1ebb\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">15 gram t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">500 gram b\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">60 gram n\u1ea5m r\u01a1m\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">100ml n\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea7m x\u01b0\u01a1ng\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 qu\u1ea3 tr\u1ee9ng v\u1ecbt mu\u1ed1i\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00f9i t\u00e0u, h\u00e0nh g\u1eebng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gia v\u1ecb<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n:\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh n\u1ea5u ch\u00e1o y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 theo c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc sau:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Ng\u00e2m t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn v\u00e0 g\u1ea1o\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cho g\u1ea1o t\u1ebb v\u00e0 g\u1ea1o n\u1ebfu tr\u1ed9n \u0111\u1ec1u, vo qua 1-2 l\u1ea7n n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ng\u00e2m g\u1ea1o qua \u0111\u00eam. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o tinh th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ng\u00e2m v\u00e0o n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb 20-30 ph\u00fat cho s\u1ee3i y\u1ebfn n\u1edf \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u01a1i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay. C\u00f2n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn th\u00f4 th\u00ec c\u1ea7n ng\u00e2m trong n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb 1-2 gi\u1edd sau \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf h\u1ebft c\u00e1c t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: H\u1ea5p b\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110em b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 \u0111i h\u1ea5p, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00e1ch l\u1ea5y th\u1ecbt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3o qua v\u1edbi d\u1ea7u \u0103n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 kh\u00f4 th\u00ec nh\u1edb r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch, ng\u00e2m trong n\u01b0\u1edbc kho\u1ea3ng 20 ph\u00fat, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111em h\u1ea5p c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7y \u0111\u1ebfn khi b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 m\u1ec1m th\u00ec t\u1eaft b\u1ebfp.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: S\u01a1 ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ea5m r\u01a1m b\u1ecf ch\u00e2n, r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 b\u0103m nh\u1ecf. Rau m\u00f9i t\u00e0u v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111em r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch, th\u00e1i nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u00e1t ri\u00eang. Tr\u1ee9ng v\u1ecbt mu\u1ed1i lu\u1ed9c ch\u00edn, t\u00e1ch ri\u00eang l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ecf \u0111em nghi\u1ec1n nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 x\u00e0o c\u00f9ng d\u1ea7u \u0103n t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p s\u00e1nh m\u1ecbn.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Ch\u01b0ng y\u1ebfn\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi y\u1ebfn n\u1edf \u0111\u1ec1u th\u00ec v\u1edbt \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e1o. Cho n\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1eadp v\u1eeba l\u01b0\u1ee3ng y\u1ebfn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ch\u01b0ng c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7y trong v\u00f2ng kho\u1ea3ng 15-20 ph\u00fat. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt m\u00f9i tanh c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho th\u00eam v\u00e0i l\u00e1t g\u1eebng ch\u01b0ng c\u00f9ng y\u1ebfn.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: N\u1ea5u ch\u00e1o y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cho g\u1ea1o v\u00e0o n\u1ed3i n\u1ea5u ch\u00e1o, sau \u0111\u00f3 cho ti\u1ebfp n\u01b0\u1edbc x\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ninh cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi g\u1ea1o m\u1ec1m. N\u00eam n\u1ebfm gia v\u1ecb v\u1eeba \u0103n r\u1ed3i cho n\u1ea5m r\u01a1m, khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ninh. Khi ch\u00e1o s\u00f4i l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp theo th\u00ec ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh cho b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 v\u00e0o \u0111un. Sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u00fac ch\u00e1o ra b\u00e1t, cho th\u00eam h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p tr\u1ee9ng mu\u1ed1n, y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00ean tr\u00ean, r\u1eafc th\u00eam h\u00e0nh, m\u00f9i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat ti\u00eau l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c ngay.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>2. S\u00fap b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn th\u01a1m ngon\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2318\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2318\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2318\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-2.jpg\" alt=\"yen sao bao ngu 2\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-2.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-2-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-2-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2318\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i style=\"font-size: 16px;\">S\u00fap b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn<\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">500 gram b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 (6 &#8211; 7 con)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">10 gram t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn (1 t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">500 gram x\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">20 gram t\u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">60 gram n\u1ea5m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00f4 (n\u1ea5m h\u01b0\u01a1ng)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1,5 L n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u00f4 m\u1ef9\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 c\u1ee7 h\u00e0nh t\u00edm<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">20 gram g\u1eebng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gia v\u1ecb<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: X\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e0 mua v\u1ec1 s\u01a1 ch\u1ebf qua, sau \u0111\u00f3 cho v\u00e0o n\u1ed3i \u0111un c\u00f9ng 1,5L n\u01b0\u1edbc trong kho\u1ea3ng 40 ph\u00fat th\u00ec cho x\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ri\u00eang. T\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn \u0111em ng\u00e2m n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ea1ch t\u1eeb 1-2 gi\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn n\u1edf \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u01a1i th\u00ec v\u1edbt ra \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e1o. N\u1ea5m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00f4 \u0111em b\u1ecf g\u1ed1c v\u00e0 r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch. B\u1eafp ng\u00f4 r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch, ng\u00e2m v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1i lo\u00e3ng sau \u0111\u00f3 r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e1o.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: B\u00e0o ng\u01b0 \u0111em t\u00e1ch b\u1ecf v\u1ecf l\u1ea5y ru\u1ed9t, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111em r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbp c\u00f9ng b\u1ed9t canh, h\u1ea1t n\u00eam, d\u1ea7u m\u00e8 v\u00e0 ti\u00eau trong v\u00f2ng 20 ph\u00fat. Sau \u0111\u00f3, cho b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 v\u00e0o n\u1ed3i n\u01b0\u1edbc ninh x\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e0 n\u1ea5u v\u1edbi l\u1eeda nh\u1ecf trong kho\u1ea3ng 30 ph\u00fat.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Cho t\u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0o n\u1ea5u trong v\u00f2ng 5 ph\u00fat th\u00ec cho ti\u1ebfp ng\u00f4 m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 n\u1ea5m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00f4 \u0111un trong v\u00f2ng 15 ph\u00fat r\u1ed3i t\u1eaft b\u1ebfp\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: M\u00fac h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p b\u00e0o ng\u01b0, b\u1eafp, t\u00e1o v\u00e0 n\u1ea5m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00f4 v\u1eeba \u0111un v\u00e0o b\u00e1t \u0111\u1ef1ng t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn. Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ch\u01b0ng c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7y h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean trong v\u00f2ng 20 ph\u00fat \u1edf nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m m\u00f9i tanh c\u1ee7a y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u00e1t g\u1eebng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u01b0ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><b>3. B\u00e0o ng\u01b0 vi c\u00e1 y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2319\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2319\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2319 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-1-vi-ca.jpg\" alt=\"M\u00f3n b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 vi c\u00e1 y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-1-vi-ca.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-1-vi-ca-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-bao-ngu-1-vi-ca-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2319\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i style=\"font-size: 16px;\">M\u00f3n b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 vi c\u00e1 y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o\u00a0<\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">G\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong 8 m\u00f3n b\u00e1t tr\u00e2n qu\u00fd, b\u00e0o ng\u01b0- vi c\u00e1 &#8211; y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m qu\u00fd hi\u1ebfm, c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cao. Vi c\u00e1 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, gi\u00fap s\u00e1ng m\u1eaft v\u00e0 ch\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn x\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1edbp. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng sinh l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng suy nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a 3 nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n \u0103n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn m\u00f3n \u0103n n\u00e0y theo c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3 gram y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">100 gram vi c\u00e1\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">150 gram b\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ea5m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00f4\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1,5L n\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00f9ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">100 gram b\u1ed9t n\u0103ng\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gia v\u1ecb\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: \u0110em vi c\u00e1 ng\u00e2m trong n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda ng\u00e0y, khi vi c\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec1m ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh h\u1ea5p c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7y vi c\u00e1 c\u00f9ng g\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1edbt m\u00f9i tanh. N\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o tinh ch\u1ebf th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ng\u00e2m trong 20-30 ph\u00fat l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o th\u00f4 th\u00ec c\u1ea7n ng\u00e2m v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc 1-2 ti\u1ebfng sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbt ra \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf h\u1ebft l\u00f4ng y\u1ebfn v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: B\u00e0o ng\u01b0 \u0111em r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch, mang h\u1ea7m trong kho\u1ea3ng 1 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u1ec1m th\u00ec t\u1eaft b\u1ebfp r\u1ed3i \u0111em th\u00e1i m\u1ecfng. N\u1ea5m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00f4 ng\u00e2m n\u01b0\u1edbc cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u1ec1m v\u00e0 \u0111em \u0111i th\u00e1i nh\u1ecf.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Cho 1,5L n\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00f9ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f9i g\u00e0 v\u00e0 x\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ed1ng \u0111em \u0111un s\u00f4i. Sau khi th\u1ecbt g\u00e0 m\u1ec1m th\u00ec v\u1edbt x\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 g\u00e0 ra, cho l\u00f2ng tr\u1eafng tr\u1ee9ng v\u00e0o khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u tay theo m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u. Cho ti\u1ebfp b\u1ed9t n\u0103ng v\u00e0o trong n\u1ed3i, n\u00eam n\u1ebfm gia v\u1ecb v\u1eeba \u0103n r\u1ed3i \u0111un ti\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1eeda nh\u1ecf trong v\u00f2ng 10 ph\u00fat. Sau \u0111\u00f3 cho h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p vi c\u00e1 m\u1eadp, b\u00e0o ng\u01b0, y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o v\u00e0 n\u1ea5m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00f4 v\u00e0o \u0111un ti\u1ebfp \u00edt ph\u00fat th\u00ec t\u1eaft b\u1ebfp.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><b>T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f3n \u0103n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cao, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2320\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2320\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2320 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-vi-ca.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-vi-ca.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-vi-ca-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-vi-ca-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2320\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba ung th\u01b0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3: Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc cho th\u1ea5y trong chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t n\u1ed9i t\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a kh\u1ed1i u. Ngo\u00e0i ra, trong <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/\">t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn<\/a> c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9a m\u1ed9t h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o t\u1ef1 do, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba s\u1ef1 l\u00e2y lan c\u1ee7a t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ung th\u01b0 sang c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan kh\u00e1c trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh tim m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch: B\u00e0o ng\u01b0 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i axit b\u00e9o nh\u01b0 omega-3, axit eicosapentaenoic (EPA) v\u00e0 axit docosahexaenoic (DHA). C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i axit n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1eafc c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh tim m\u1ea1ch. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i protein c\u00f3 trong y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n sinh t\u1ebf b\u00e0o B. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i t\u1ebf b\u00e0o kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sinh ra kh\u00e1ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng m\u00e1u: Phosphorus c\u00f3 trong b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tu\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n trong m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o b\u1ecb hao m\u00f2n c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn protein v\u00e0 s\u1eaft gi\u00fap t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o h\u1ed3ng c\u1ea7u nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n sinh ra \u0111\u1ee7 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e1u cung c\u1ea5p cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn <\/span><b>y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o b\u00e0o ng\u01b0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u00e0 Lifenest mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc. Hy v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n ngon v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng!<\/span><br \/>\nXem th\u00eam:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/ke-hoach-kinh-doanh-yen\/\">B\u1eadt m\u00ed k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch kinh doanh y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 100%<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o v\u00e0 b\u00e0o ng\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cao. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f3n \u0103n ngon, b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn t\u1eeb 2 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Lifenest s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2317,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_seopress_robots_primary_cat":"none"},"categories":[19],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2315"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2315"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2315\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3895,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2315\/revisions\/3895"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2317"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2315"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2315"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2315"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}